Language name: Tamasheq
Language number: 4357
Alternate names: Tuareg
Classification: Afro-Asiatic, Berber
Comments: All consonants may appear long (geminate).  
Prasse's description indicates that there are five 
long/short vowel pairs and two vowels that only occur 
short, but details are unclear.

Sources: 

Prasse, K-G. 1972. Manuel de Grammaire Touaregue. 
Akademisk Forlag, Copenhagen.